OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Frain will clear northeast through the
OL,7,Fevening. Then it will stay dry for the
OL,8,Frest of the night with clear spells
OL,9,Fand perhaps the odd fog patch by dawn.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FSome bright spells possible
OL,12,Fat first, but soon clouding over with
OL,13,Fshowery outbreaks of rain, these
OL,14,Fturning heavy in places in the
OL,15,Fafternoon. A little less warm than
OL,16,FFriday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
