OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fon Sunday with a chance of showers.
OL,7,FRain for a time on Monday, otherwise
OL,8,Fsunny spells and a few showers
OL,9,Fcontinuing through Tuesday. Remaining
OL,10,Fcooler with some overnight frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
